chat_history: POLITICAL AID #1: Look at Anheuser. Anyone would think he was President. Did you hear, he wants us to sign in and out like school boys?
ADRIAN: I still can't believe that Wilson chose him of all people to run the White House.
POLITICAL AID #2: Why not? Anheuser owns the Senate and the Congress.
ADRIAN: Shame he's such a pompous ass.
Narrator: Adrian turns to see Anheuser smiling.
ADRIAN: We were talking about what a great speech you gave tonight. Well done, sir.
ANHEUSER: It's Helmsley, right? I'll remember that.
Narrator: Anheuser walks away with a dangerous smile.
POLITICAL AID #2: That guy scares the shit out of me.
Narrator: At that moment Adrian's cell phone rings.
PROF. WEST: I've been trying to reach you!
